Selamat pagi semua.

5
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,360
Sini ialah Kampung Fu Gua.

6
00:01:34,539 --> 00:01:35,470
Hari ini berawan.

7
00:01:35,620 --> 00:01:37,610
Suhu purata 23 darjah,

8
00:01:37,930 --> 00:01:38,810
ia cuaca yang baik.

9
00:01:38,900 --> 00:01:39,460
Ah.

10
00:01:39,460 --> 00:01:40,530
Ia cuaca yang baik.

11
00:01:57,660 --> 00:01:59,300
Menyiarkan satu iklan.

12
00:01:59,420 --> 00:02:01,300
Kedai runcit Su Qiao

13
00:02:01,450 --> 00:02:04,250
melancarkan banyak promosi baru-baru ini.

14
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:07,000
Beli secukup 20 yuan, dapat sepaket tisu secara percuma.

15
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:07,760
Tanda kurung,

16
00:02:07,860 --> 00:02:10,580
kuota terhad tapi jangan beritahu semua orang.

17
00:02:10,820 --> 00:02:11,320
Tanda kurung.

18
00:02:13,690 --> 00:02:15,030
Saya tak sengaja membacanya.

19
00:02:39,610 --> 00:02:40,990
Bapa saudara, bangunlah!

20
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:50,790
Bapa saudara, bangunlah!

21
00:02:50,860 --> 00:02:52,380
Cepat bangun dan buka pintu untuk kedai runcit!

22
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:55,390
Kak Qiao, bukankah kita

23
00:02:55,420 --> 00:02:56,660
buka kedai runcit supaya

24
00:02:56,660 --> 00:02:59,190
boleh buka pada masa yang diingini?

25
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:01,820
Kalau tak boleh buat sesuka hati,

26
00:03:01,820 --> 00:03:03,570
ia tak bermakna lagi.

27
00:03:03,570 --> 00:03:04,360
Hu Zhifei!

28
00:03:05,340 --> 00:03:06,670
Mak awak serahkan awak kepada saya

29
00:03:06,790 --> 00:03:08,530
bukan untuk biar saya lihat awak jadi semakin teruk.

30
00:03:08,740 --> 00:03:10,220
Itulah nenek awak.

31
00:03:10,770 --> 00:03:12,630
Ibu awak, iaitu kakak saya.

32
00:03:12,660 --> 00:03:14,010
Serahkan awak kepada saya

33
00:03:14,100 --> 00:03:16,260
supaya kita berdua saling bergantung,

34
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:17,700
bukan saling menyakiti.

35
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:20,170
Awak simpan pisau itu dulu.

36
00:03:22,140 --> 00:03:23,100
Awak cakap,

37
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:24,900
kenapa kita buka kedai runcit?

38
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:25,620
Cari wang!

39
00:03:25,860 --> 00:03:27,020
Prinsip kehidupan saya

40
00:03:27,020 --> 00:03:28,150
adalah untuk cari wang!

41
00:03:28,300 --> 00:03:29,700
Semua makna hidup saya

42
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:30,660
adalah cari wang,

43
00:03:30,660 --> 00:03:31,340
cari wang,

44
00:03:31,340 --> 00:03:32,100
dan cari wang lagi!

45
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:33,340
Saya pergi buka pintu sekarang!

46
00:03:33,340 --> 00:03:33,710
Ya.

47
00:03:39,610 --> 00:03:40,550
Masa untuk hantar barang.

48
00:03:41,410 --> 00:03:42,100
Kak Qiao,

49
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:43,650
bilakah awak boleh tukar

50
00:03:43,670 --> 00:03:44,660
nada dering telefon...

51
00:03:44,660 --> 00:03:46,100
Batu gunting kertas!

52
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,079
Awak gunakan helah!

53
00:03:48,900 --> 00:03:49,980
Mengaku kalah.

54
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,570
Awak yang keluarkan batu sendiri.

55
00:03:52,140 --> 00:03:52,800
Oh.

56
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:54,150
Hari ini awak hantar barang.

57
00:03:54,620 --> 00:03:57,100
Jangan lupa hantar khinzir itu ke Keluarga Fang.

58
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:58,340
Ia bukan bernama "khinzir itu".

59
00:03:58,550 --> 00:03:59,980
Ia dipanggil Cha Shao.
[Nota: Cha Shao bermaksud "daging khinzir barbeku"]

60
00:04:07,020 --> 00:04:09,320
Cha Shao, saya datang hantar awak balik ke rumah.

61
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:13,870
[Kedai Runcit Fu Rui]

62
00:04:10,020 --> 00:04:11,650
Bapa saudara, saya pergi hantar barang!

63
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,880
Pandu perlahan-lahan.

64
00:04:21,820 --> 00:04:25,490
Nama saya Su Qiao. Saya pelajar Tingkatan 5 di Sekolah Menengah Pekan Fu Gua.

65
00:04:26,210 --> 00:04:26,950
Sini ialah

66
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:30,720
Pekan Fu Gua, Kampung Fu Gua yang saya tinggal sejak kecil.

67
00:04:30,940 --> 00:04:32,070
Tak dikira sangat kaya.

68
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:35,909
Nasib baik ada gunung, laut, lembu dan ikan.

69
00:04:36,180 --> 00:04:38,310
Musim panas sangat lembap, musim sejuk tak sejuk.

70
00:04:38,740 --> 00:04:40,850
Semua orang hidup dengan angat gembira.

71
00:04:41,250 --> 00:04:44,130
Ia sebuah kampung kecil di selatan yang hidup dengan aman.

72
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:48,100
Ada kawasan perniagaan pusat di bandar besar.

73
00:04:48,820 --> 00:04:51,540
Kampung Fu Gua pula ada kedai runcit keluarga saya.

74
00:04:52,140 --> 00:04:55,000
Kedai runcit menyokong kelancaran operasi

75
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:57,380
[Kedai Runcit Fu Rui]

76
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:58,240
barangan keperluan harian seluruh Kampung Fu Gua.

77
00:04:58,620 --> 00:05:01,240
Ia tempat yang paling penting di seluruh kampung.

78
00:05:01,420 --> 00:05:04,280
Saya pula orang yang paling penting di kedai runcit.

79
00:05:04,970 --> 00:05:05,700
Jadi,

80
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:06,640
saya,

81
00:05:06,980 --> 00:05:07,690
Su Qiao,

82
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:10,750
ialah orang yang paling penting di seluruh Kampung Fu Gua.

83
00:05:30,670 --> 00:05:31,780
[Ayah]

84
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:38,170
[Pengarah Lin]

85
00:05:36,900 --> 00:05:39,640
Awak dah hebat, lagi letakkan panggilan saya.

86
00:05:40,060 --> 00:05:41,980
Saya tak tahu apa yang awak fikirkan.

87
00:05:42,420 --> 00:05:44,020
Walaupun saya tak bersetuju sebelum ini,

88
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,750
awak juga mahu jadi artis tak kira apa-apa.

89
00:05:46,010 --> 00:05:46,850
Dah berlatih begitu lama,

90
00:05:46,850 --> 00:05:48,340
sekarang bersuah payah dah bertambah baik

91
00:05:48,340 --> 00:05:49,700
dan ada orang cari awak untuk berlakon.

92
00:05:49,700 --> 00:05:50,720
Awak terus

93
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,860
larikan diri sebaliknya.

94
00:05:52,620 --> 00:05:53,740
Saya tak mahu berlakon

95
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:54,740
dan tak mahu jadi artis.

96
00:05:55,100 --> 00:05:56,700
Awak ini tak fikir sebelum buat sesuatu.

97
00:05:57,740 --> 00:05:59,020
Sudahlah jika awak tak nak jadi artis.

98
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:01,460
Saya tak bercadang nak biar awak jadi artis pada asalnya.

99
00:06:02,060 --> 00:06:03,910
Awak berada di kampung untuk sementara dulu.

100
00:06:04,060 --> 00:06:05,840
Saya akan bincang tentang pembatalan kontrak dengan syarikat awak beberapa hari ini.

101
00:06:05,860 --> 00:06:07,060
Awak tak perlu pedulikan pembatalan kontrak.

102
00:06:07,140 --> 00:06:07,930
Saya boleh uruskannya dengan baik.

103
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,070
Awak boleh uruskan apa dengan baik?

104
00:06:09,460 --> 00:06:11,140
Awak tak boleh lakukan apa-apa dengan baik.

105
00:06:11,140 --> 00:06:12,940
Langsung tak bertanggungjawab terhadap diri sendiri.

106
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:14,660
Saya nak lihat macam mana dengan awak kelak.

107
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:17,220
Lembu siapa?

108
00:06:17,660 --> 00:06:19,180
Helo?

109
00:06:20,380 --> 00:06:21,370
Kenapa awak diam?

110
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:24,480
Hantar sampai sini saja.

111
00:06:24,770 --> 00:06:25,710
Awak dengar tak?

112
00:07:15,900 --> 00:07:17,070
Datuk, saya dah datang!

113
00:07:17,550 --> 00:07:18,090
Qiao!

114
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:20,080
Saya dah bawa semua barangan yang Pak Cik Zhang

115
00:07:20,100 --> 00:07:20,950
suruh saya beli untuk datuk.

116
00:07:21,740 --> 00:07:22,780
Masih ada banyak barang di rumah,

117
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:24,620
suruh dia jangan bazirkan wang lagi.

118
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:27,960
Kenapa?

119
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:31,320
Ada seorang budak melangkah padi di sawah padi.

120
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:32,260
Awak pergi lihat.

121
00:07:32,780 --> 00:07:34,820
Datuk, tak apa. Saya pergi lihat.

122
00:07:34,820 --> 00:07:35,900
Baik, cepat pergi.

123
00:08:02,380 --> 00:08:03,300
Awak jangan terus berjalan lagi!

124
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:04,300
Awak akan merosakkan padi!

125
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:05,220
Hei!

126
00:08:08,740 --> 00:08:10,470
Saya sedang bercakap dengan awak!

127
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:13,140
Awak pekak? Saya sedang bercakap dengan awak!

128
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:27,010
Abang.

129
00:08:27,140 --> 00:08:28,770
Saya suruh awak jangan jalan ke depan, awak tak dengar?

130
00:08:28,820 --> 00:08:30,110
Buat saya makan tanah.

131
00:08:30,150 --> 00:08:30,660
Ada orang terjatuh,

132
00:08:30,660 --> 00:08:31,660
tapi awak tak papahnya.

133
00:08:31,660 --> 00:08:32,500
Kenapa awak begini?

134
00:08:32,530 --> 00:08:33,450
Awak bersivik tak?

135
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:43,299
Awak rosakkannya.

136
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,760
Awak juga merosakkan sawah padi.

137
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:50,000
[Sekolah Menengah Fu Gua, Su Qiao, Kelas 3 Tingkatan 5]

138
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:51,330
Tengok apa?

139
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:57,320
Nama awak Su Qiao?

140
00:08:58,060 --> 00:08:59,590
Ya, kenapa?

141
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:03,570
Nama saya Lin Zilu.

142
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,330
Saya tak tanya nama awak juga.

143
00:09:13,060 --> 00:09:13,540
Hei!

144
00:09:15,780 --> 00:09:16,640
Orang apa ini?

145
00:09:17,510 --> 00:09:18,660
Peliknya.

146
00:09:26,060 --> 00:09:29,090
[Sekolah Menengah Fu Gua, Bandar Mei Gang]

147
00:09:50,370 --> 00:09:52,290
Habislah, saya akan lewat.

148
00:09:53,340 --> 00:09:54,510
Bagaimana? Boleh letak sekarang?

149
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:55,900
Cikgu masih merayau-rayau di sana.

150
00:10:01,060 --> 00:10:02,860
Dah terlambat, masih mengkaji semut.

151
00:10:02,860 --> 00:10:04,480
Jika komet melanggar bumi suatu hari nanti,

152
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:06,310
perlu tak awak pergi ke tandas dulu sebelum lari?

153
00:10:07,700 --> 00:10:08,900
Selalu lewat

154
00:10:08,900 --> 00:10:10,420
tapi semut berpindah rumah tak biasa dijumpa.

155
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:11,420
Baik, cepat bangun.

156
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,320
Kenapa dengan baju ini?

157
00:10:14,540 --> 00:10:15,140
Dah makan tahi?

158
00:10:15,170 --> 00:10:16,070
Kenapa awak cakap begitu?

159
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:18,130
Saya terserempak dengan seorang pembawa malang dalam perjalanan hari ini.

160
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:19,180
Malangnya.

161
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:20,620
Jom, sekaranglah masanya! Jom!

162
00:10:24,780 --> 00:10:26,380
Tolong saya ambil beg, berhati-hati.

163
00:10:28,300 --> 00:10:29,420
Bau apa ini?

164
00:10:29,420 --> 00:10:30,540
- Takkan memang ada tahi?
- Jangan peduli.

165
00:10:30,540 --> 00:10:32,210
Di dalamnya ada barang kegemaran saya.

166
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:35,090
Jom!

167
00:10:41,220 --> 00:10:42,380
Lihat pergerakan abang.

168
00:10:43,690 --> 00:10:45,610
Senang, tangkas.

169
00:10:47,580 --> 00:10:48,150
Fang Liang.

170
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:50,190
Tak bawa kad nama, tolak dua markah.

171
00:10:49,050 --> 00:10:50,690
[Pengawas]

172
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:51,730
Jangan. Saya dah pakai.

173
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:01,410
Saya tahu kamu akan lewat.

174
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:03,050
Jadi, saya sengaja mengumpan cikgu ke tempat lain.

175
00:11:03,620 --> 00:11:04,130
Ikut saya.

176
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:05,180
Ketua kelas memang hebat.

177
00:11:06,220 --> 00:11:07,630
Saya, Su Qiao.

178
00:11:08,140 --> 00:11:09,560
Ketua kelas, Guan Jinjin.

179
00:11:09,820 --> 00:11:10,840
Si tinggi, Fang Liang.

180
00:11:11,020 --> 00:11:12,570
Dan juga Ikan Duri, Wang Nianyu.
[Nota: "Ikan duri" dan "Nianyu" ada sebutan sama]

181
00:11:13,100 --> 00:11:15,910
Kamilah Kumpulan Terhebat yang paling terkenal

182
00:11:16,140 --> 00:11:17,950
di Kampung Fu Gua.

183
00:11:21,900 --> 00:11:24,220
[Kelas 3 Tingkatan 5]

184
00:11:21,900 --> 00:11:24,220
[Sekolah Menengah Fu Gua, Bandar Mei Gang]

185
00:11:31,980 --> 00:11:32,950
Kenapa awak bawa ini?

186
00:11:34,420 --> 00:11:36,530
Sepatutnya hantar ke rumah awak pagi ini,

187
00:11:36,950 --> 00:11:38,910
tapi saya terserempak dengan seorang pembawa malang.

188
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,210
Dia buatkan saya terjatuh ke sawah padi dan terkena lumpur.

189
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:42,490
Jadi, saya tak sempat.

190
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:45,810
- Bagi awak sekarang.
- Jangan bagi saya.

191
00:11:45,830 --> 00:11:46,610
Macam mana jika ia menjerit?

192
00:11:46,610 --> 00:11:47,420
Takkan begitu.

193
00:11:47,820 --> 00:11:49,060
Saya beri ia sikit arak masakan,

194
00:11:49,060 --> 00:11:50,060
ia tidur lena.

195
00:11:50,060 --> 00:11:50,660
Tak boleh.

196
00:11:50,660 --> 00:11:51,820
Jika diketahui oleh Cikgu Yu,

197
00:11:51,820 --> 00:11:52,880
saya akan dipukul oleh abang ngah dan abang lang.

198
00:11:53,210 --> 00:11:54,260
Pukullah awak sampai mati jika begitu.

199
00:11:57,040 --> 00:11:58,120
Jangan pandang saya.

200
00:11:58,610 --> 00:11:59,340
Saya tak peduli.

201
00:12:01,380 --> 00:12:02,060
Jangan pandang saya!

202
00:12:02,940 --> 00:12:04,140
Awak yang bawa, awak bertanggungjawab sendiri.

203
00:12:04,580 --> 00:12:05,210
Putus hubungan!

204
00:12:06,370 --> 00:12:07,600
Jangan.

205
00:12:07,740 --> 00:12:08,950
Bukankah tiada orang di situ?

206
00:12:09,220 --> 00:12:09,960
Letak ke dalam laci meja.

207
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:19,410
Kenapa?

208
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:21,100
Bos Su, bagi sebotol Cola.

209
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:23,760
Bayar dulu.

210
00:12:27,740 --> 00:12:29,680
Perniagaan Bos Su bagus.

211
00:12:29,860 --> 00:12:31,220
Berapa harga botol Cola ini?

212
00:12:35,860 --> 00:12:38,180
Mana boleh minta wang?

213
00:12:38,220 --> 00:12:39,940
Cikgu Yu begitu letih dalam kelas.

214
00:12:40,190 --> 00:12:41,690
Minum sesuap Cola untuk berkumur.

215
00:12:41,830 --> 00:12:43,820
Saya lihat awak ini semakin berani.

216
00:12:43,970 --> 00:12:44,810
Cepat simpan!

217
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:48,790
Jika saya tangkap awak jual barang lain kali,

218
00:12:48,830 --> 00:12:49,860
saya akan rampas semuanya!

219
00:12:51,460 --> 00:12:51,960
Gula!

220
00:13:04,580 --> 00:13:05,980
Sebelum kelas bermula,

221
00:13:06,100 --> 00:13:08,420
biar saya perkenalkan pelajar baharu

222
00:13:08,420 --> 00:13:09,780
yang dipindahkan ke kelas kita.

223
00:13:10,370 --> 00:13:11,020
Masuklah.

224
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:25,450
Inilah pembawa malang yang saya katakan.

225
00:13:27,660 --> 00:13:28,870
Dia agak kacak.

226
00:13:30,250 --> 00:13:31,980
Masih tak malu untuk gelar diri sendiri sebagai lelaki paling kacak di sekolah?

227
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:34,650
Baiklah.

228
00:13:35,130 --> 00:13:36,800
Awak perkenalkan diri dulu.

229
00:13:38,680 --> 00:13:39,540
Nama saya Lin Zilu.

230
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:48,530
Awak duduk di sanalah.

231
00:13:49,170 --> 00:13:49,890
Saya tak nak!

232
00:13:51,140 --> 00:13:53,820
Su Qiao. Awak dah lama jadi bos,

233
00:13:53,820 --> 00:13:55,220
awak ingat keluarga awak yang buka sekolah ini?

234
00:13:56,050 --> 00:13:56,750
Duduk!

235
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:00,490
Jangan pedulikan dia.

236
00:14:00,860 --> 00:14:01,670
Awak duduk di sana.

237
00:14:02,070 --> 00:14:03,370
Jika dia berani buli awak,

238
00:14:03,630 --> 00:14:04,410
awak beritahu saya.

239
00:14:06,710 --> 00:14:07,510
Terima kasih, cikgu.

240
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:14,680
Kelas yang lepas,

241
00:14:14,900 --> 00:14:17,860
kita berhenti di perenggan kedua "Preface to the Poems Composed at the Orchid Pavilion".

242
00:14:19,060 --> 00:14:20,300
Murid mana yang boleh imbas kembali

